name: Ectodash
description:
Made for Jamcraft 7

The Arcane Delights Brewery & Cauldron Shop makes the finest undead brew! Too bad the humans aren't here to see it....

Gather Ingerdients for the Witch Chef according to order in your shitty 9 to 5' while avoiding pesky Crim Spirits. What has your afterlife become....?

!!VERY UNFINISHED!!
